Implemented Work Tracker module - backend data model and API for personal productivity tracking.

Created TrackerEntry model with fields: id, type (work_session/deadline/note), raw_text, duration, category, due_date, estimated_minutes, timestamps.

Added API endpoints:
- POST/GET/PUT/DELETE /api/tracker/entries (CRUD operations)
- GET /api/tracker/entries?type=X (filter by type)
- GET /api/tracker/summary (statistics: total entries, work sessions, total minutes, deadlines, categories breakdown, last 7 days)
- GET /api/tracker/deadlines (list deadlines with upcoming filter)

Created migration script and applied to database. Added Pydantic schemas for request/response validation. Wrote 12 comprehensive tests covering all endpoints and edge cases.

Tests: 21/21 passed (9 existing tracker item tests + 12 new tracker entry tests)
